                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6" style="text-align: center;"><div class="fb-page" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/DungeonStoreOficial" data-small-header="false" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="true" data-show-posts="false"><div class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><blockquote cite="https://www.facebook.com/DungeonStoreOficial"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/DungeonStoreOficial">Dungeon Store</a></blockquote></div></div></div>
                </div>
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
                <h4>2. Se inscreva no canal da Dungeon Store</h4>
                <script src="https://apis.google.com/js/platform.js"></script>

                <div style="text-align: center;"><div class="g-ytsubscribe" data-channelid="UCi8keikVSqQg8LIC3s92OZA" data-layout="full" data-count="default"></div></div>
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
                <h4>3.Marque 3 amigos na publicação abaixo e a compartilhe em modo PÚBLICO</h4>
                <div style="text-align: center"><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/20531316728/posts/10154009990506729/" data-width="500"><div class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><blockquote cite="https://www.facebook.com/20531316728/posts/10154009990506729/">Posted by <a href="https://www.facebook.com/facebook/">Facebook</a> on&nbsp;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/20531316728/posts/10154009990506729/">Thursday, August 27, 2015</a></blockquote></div></div></div>
